OL,3,GNEWSCBBC News channel to expand UK
OL,4,Celection coverage with special
OL,5,Cprogramming
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe BBC News channel is set to
OL,8,Fsignificantly increase its coverage of
OL,9,Fthis week's UK elections, with a series
OL,10,Fof on-air changes coming into effect
OL,11,Ffrom Tuesday.
OL,13,FThe channel's UK feed will split from
OL,14,Fits international core output for much
OL,15,Fof the day on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,16,Fbetween 9am and 6pm, to allow for
OL,17,Fdedicated domestic election
OL,18,Fprogramming.
OL,23,EPub: 04-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,151,140,200,120,0,100
