SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F150A1781979086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCBBC News channel to expand UK
OL,4,Celection coverage with special
OL,5,Cprogramming
OL,6,
OL,7,FChristian Fraser will anchor the
OL,8,Fcoverage from Studio C, with politics
OL,9,Fguests featured every hour throughout
OL,10,Fthe day.
OL,12,FPresenter Pria Rai will also be on hand
OL,13,Fto guide viewers through live political
OL,14,Fevents as they happen.
OL,16,FAlongside the extended daytime
OL,17,Fcoverage, the channel will opt out to
OL,18,FPolitics Live between 12.15pm and 1pm,
OL,19,Ffollowed by the BBC One news programme
OL,20,Ffrom 1pm.
OL,23,EPub: 04-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,151,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15003
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F150A1781979086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCBBC News channel to expand UK
OL,4,Celection coverage with special
OL,5,Cprogramming
OL,6,
OL,7,FSpecial coverage will then get underway
OL,8,Fin earnest from 11.10pm on Thursday, as
OL,9,Fresults begin to come in.
OL,11,FViewers can also expect a range of
OL,12,Fadditional content throughout the week,
OL,13,Fincluding explainer films, panel
OL,14,Fdiscussions and Your Voice segments.
OL,16,FA postcode tracker will also be
OL,17,Favailable to help audiences follow
OL,18,Fresults in their local area.
OL,23,EPub: 04-May-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
