OL,3,GNEWSCBBC News channel to expand UK
OL,4,Celection coverage with special
OL,5,Cprogramming
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe BBC says it intends to continue
OL,8,Fcovering major global stories alongside
OL,9,Fthe election, with the expanded
OL,10,Fpolitical coverage sitting alongside
OL,11,Fits usual news agenda rather than
OL,12,Freplacing it entirely.
